The '''Alderaanian Death Legion''' was a group within the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] which was made up of men and women that came from the destroyed planet of [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]]. This group was given the worst sort of missions that had a high casualty rate mainly because its members requested such assignments for a variety of motives.

